{"tid":833431,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple WatchOS 5 新錶面為實境拍攝 並非 CG 製作","createTime":"2018-09-23T13:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T16:17:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c610e0564560320a585ff462caa660be621f0cae","tid":833431,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在的 CG 技術昌明，已經不再是「有圖有真相」的年代，不過 Apple 最近在 WatchOS 5 加入的新錶面設計，卻竟然是實境拍攝而不是 CG 作品，有媒體公開了部分的製作過程，顯示製作的用心。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aK7KPw9bLfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaK7KPw9bLfI&d=AjF55Uvm8a1Lree0xpOGZi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=28d081e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aK7KPw9bLfI</a><br />\n<br />\nApple 在 WatchOS 5 加入的火、水和彩色煙霧動態錶面設計，為 Apple Watch 帶來了更多錶面選擇，而一開始看到的時候，相信不少人也會覺得是 CG 製作的效果，不過原來這些效果都是 100% 利用實境拍攝製作。在簡短的製作特輯之中，可以看到攝影師們使用模具模擬指針的位置，在加入不同的元素例如噴火或製作波浪等，拍攝錶面特效。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利用實境拍攝達到看起來應該 CG 也做到的效果，除了 Apple 之外其實 Windows 10 的預設桌面背景當時也是同樣做法，令人嘖嘖稱奇。看來在電腦特效流行的時代，科技企業也仍然願意使用傳統方式製作漂亮的圖像效果。"},{"pid":"1d94c9cc8b2ad3bad0bd1897a96f5e7ee19b23ad","tid":833431,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6669c72bbe86f20fb0d673b36789b031c2a3d9f2","tid":833431,"uid":24044,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"諗起華為用canon 影相話係自己部機"},{"pid":"b47295dfd810bb82efc2b0351bb7d140be12a9b6","tid":833431,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2282a76fd19ee00d5d66462e9e0db80ab306e86","tid":833431,"uid":9610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39a7b196e2fbac00263a7d0a6921e512d597dce","tid":833431,"uid":25517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"cls apple"},{"pid":"9c4142d564cd1997f67c2946a177425a343f533e","tid":833431,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"本身已經好想買<br />\n睇完直頭射左"},{"pid":"a053c2495f150c9f05db5b6d451d0ac9a3aae599","tid":833431,"uid":53122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"所以外國先整到精品<br />\n<br />\n支國永遠只可以山寨到個外殼"},{"pid":"3b0155bed650efbc61c2d754c777f492696bc2e6","tid":833431,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a053c2495f150c9f05db5b6d451d0ac9a3aae599","tid":833431,"uid":53122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"所以外國先整到精品<br />\n<br />\n支國永遠只可以山寨到個外殼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"屌米好意思整個1萬嘅屌米max套裝去串人，真係假係先己掉嘅"},{"pid":"ed23efe5653aa79b7dad90761407c0a56a085084","tid":833431,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我唔會買Apple錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整埋iPhone 動態背景啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668838f71eac877cc78ea0d1f60b879d4457f50d","tid":833431,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"實拍呢啲應該易過 simulation"},{"pid":"c6994c6f28a8539e88aba01dc8662528b0571028","tid":833431,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c4142d564cd1997f67c2946a177425a343f533e","tid":833431,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"